They are waiters.

https://agendaweb.org/exercises/verbs/to-be/contracted-forms
I am a boy.
I'm a boy.
You are a girl.
You're a girl.
He is my friend.
He's my friend.
She is my mother.
She's my mother.
It is a dog.
It's a dog.
We are happy.
We're happy.
You are tall.
You're tall.
They are a family.
They're a family.
